{"title":"海边一姑娘","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":2,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海边一姑娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条破旧的渔船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是她童年的摇篮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她每天见到的景物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是大海的波澜……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不幸啊！鲨鱼和海盗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞噬了溺爱她的双亲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛苦呵！泪水和仇恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌满她那才懂事的眼睛……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她撒过多少次渔网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一片鱼鳞带来幸福；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她拾过多少个海蚌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一颗珍珠带来希望……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙须树上的细须啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年比一年挨近地面；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相思树下的思念啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐渐地渐渐地飞向北边……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一天，她划着桨划着桨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来从井岗山上下来的大军；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一天，她摇着橹摇着橹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接来从延河旁边走来的士兵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她把宣传标语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散发到最东面的岛屿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她把侦察班长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"护送到敌人的前沿阵地……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在她盛鱼的船舱里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踡缩着被俘的敌军；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在她巡视的礁岩上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬上来投诚的官兵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当在晶亮的海波上面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现出她那矫健的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"居民们便会告诉自己的孩子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这位姑娘啊！值得我们尊敬……”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}